expression: plain
---
- Usage ----------------------------------------------------------------
  osp history [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>
------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Commands -------------------------------------------------------------
  list
  prune
  clear
  help   Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Options --------------------------------------------------------------
  -i, --incognito
      --profile <PROFILE>
      --no-env
      --no-config-file
      --plugin-dir <PLUGIN_DIRS>
      --theme <THEME>
      --presentation <PRESENTATION>  [possible values: expressive, compact, austere]
      --gammel-og-bitter
  -h, --help                         Print help
------------------------------------------------------------------------
